  - "③ $P(k=4)=5\\cdot\\tfrac{1}{256}\\cdot\\tfrac{3}{4}=\\tfrac{15}{1024}$; $P(k=5)=\\tfrac{1}{1024}$. Sum $=\\tfrac{16}{1024}=\\tfrac{1}{64}$."
tests:
  bernoulli: 1.0
  probability: 0.3
